{
  "id" : "features",
  "title" : "特性和优势",
  "contents" : "<div class=\"content\">\n<header class=\"marketing-banner\">\n  <h1 class=\"banner-headline no-toc no-anchor\" id=\"features--benefits\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4ia8lpk5kyaqa85yf5t4xn5ge\">特性和优势</h1>\n</header>\n<article>\n  <div class=\"flex-center\">\n    <div>\n      <div class=\"feature-section\">\n        <div class=\"feature-header\">\n          <div class=\"text-headline\">Cross Platform</div>\n          <img src=\"generated/images/marketing/features/feature-icon.svg\" height=\"70px\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"feature-row\">\n          <div class=\"feature\">\n            <div class=\"feature-title\">Progressive Web Apps</div>\n            <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"pj8fnbuyfguvs6siert0848b\">使用现代 Web 平台功能提供类似应用程序的体验。 高性能、离线和零步骤安装。</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature\">\n            <div class=\"feature-title\">Native</div>\n            <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cr4s8617ba6pyg3zlqpbkrkha\">使用 Cordova、Ionic 或 NativeScript 的策略构建原生移动应用程序。</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature\">\n            <div class=\"feature-title\">Desktop</div>\n            <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ebpn92ps1dffmpkfbcw41qxva\">使用与 Web 相同的 Angular 方法创建跨 Mac、Windows 和 Linux 的桌面安装应用程序，以及访问原生操作系统 API 的能力。</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <hr>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature-section\">\n        <div class=\"feature-header\">\n          <div class=\"text-headline\">Speed and Performance</div>\n          <img src=\"generated/images/marketing/features/feature-icon.svg\" height=\"70px\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"feature-row\">\n          <div class=\"feature\">\n            <div class=\"feature-title\">Code Generation</div>\n            <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3evocev5sx456wd2noxtoqnxn\">Angular 将你的模板转换为高度优化以适应当今 JavaScript 虚拟机的代码，让你在拥有框架的生产力的同时，也拥有手写代码的所有优势。</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature\">\n            <div class=\"feature-title\">Universal</div>\n            <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"750jtwbxkygy4u24uoj3vu9ze\">在 node.js、.NET、PHP 和其他服务器上提供应用程序的第一个视图，以便在 HTML 和 CSS 中实现近乎即时的渲染。也为优化 SEO 的网站铺平了道路。</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature\">\n            <div class=\"feature-title\">Code Splitting</div>\n            <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7gc45en8xwmvl544hqes5jzzj\">Angular 应用程序使用新的组件路由器快速加载，该路由器提供自动代码拆分，因此用户只需加载渲染他们请求的视图所需的代码。</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <hr>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature-section\">\n        <div class=\"feature-header\">\n          <div class=\"text-headline\">Productivity</div>\n          <img src=\"generated/images/marketing/features/feature-icon.svg\" height=\"70px\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"feature-row\">\n          <div class=\"feature\">\n            <div class=\"feature-title\">Templates</div>\n            <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bl9shra7wt3zawk9y9vyt9jqt\">使用简单而强大的模板语法快速创建 UI 视图。</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature\">\n            <div class=\"feature-title\">Angular CLI</div>\n            <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"14dac4dt86edvgqtr0yz1tm7d\">命令行工具：快速开始构建，添加组件和测试，然后立即部署。</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature\">\n            <div class=\"feature-title\">IDEs</div>\n            <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7a5ymr1nm9i64wph1g0tzwas6\">在流行的编辑器和 IDE 中获得智能代码补全、即时错误和其他反馈。</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <hr>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"feature-section\">\n        <div class=\"feature-header\">\n          <div class=\"text-headline\">Full Development Story</div>\n          <img src=\"generated/images/marketing/features/feature-icon.svg\" height=\"70px\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"feature-row\">\n          <div class=\"feature\">\n            <div class=\"feature-title\">Testing</div>\n            <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"73mqfofa9tm0os8ubw58dmiau\">使用 Karma 进行单元测试，你可以在每次保存时就知道是否破坏了代码。Protractor 使你的场景测试运行得更快，并且更加稳定。</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature\">\n            <div class=\"feature-title\">Animation</div>\n            <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8v8j17gqy16l6uyw3z8ci61y3\">通过 Angular 直观的 API，使用很少的代码创建高性能、复杂的编排和动画时间线。</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"feature\">\n            <div class=\"feature-title\">Accessibility</div>\n            <p class=\"text-body\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8be35huczhth9nkkchbew6tj1\">使用支持 ARIA 的组件、开发人员指南和内置的 a11y 测试基础设施创建无障碍应用程序。</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"cta-bar announcement-bar\">\n    <a class=\"button\" href=\"guide/quickstart\">Get Started</a>\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n</div>\n<!-- links to this doc:\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - guide/quickstart\n-->"
}